                    <p class="about-me-text"><span>Hello &#128400;</span> Call me Sammy, the creator of SAFITNESS. I was
                        born and raised in West Africa/Ghana. Currently live in Philadelphia. My goal is to help any
                        individual to reach their fitness goals regardless of their situation. With 5 years of training
                        experience, I’ve come to realize the skills and tools you need to maximize your fitness results
                        within a short period of duration</p>

                    <h4 class="p-title">Nutrition </h4>
                    <p class="about-me-text">Beginning of my fitness journey, I wasn’t strict with my diet at all. Over
                        time
                        I realized my NUTRITION plays a huge role in my journey which is why I’ve created nutrition
                        plans to
                        help any individual. </p>
                    <h4 class="p-title">Style of Training </h4>
                    <p class="about-me-text">Every individual has their own specific needs so everyone should receive a
                        plan
                        that suits their goals. Throughout the selection of plans, you'll see that some are completely
                        bodyweight along with plans that require gym access. Whether you're new to fitness or an expert,
                        let
                        one of my plans take you to that next level you're trying to achieve. Also, I want everyone to
                        know
                        they are unique and have the potential to achieve any of their personal goals. The only thing
                        they
                        need is a <strong>PLAN</strong> , <strong>CONSISTENCY</strong>, <strong>DEDICATION</strong> &
                        the
                        right
                        <strong>MINDSET</strong>.
                    </p>
                    <p class="about-me-text">Moreover, I want as many people as possible to realize that you will only
                        own
                        one body and the faster you take full control of it, the longer and better you will live. </p>
                    <p class="about-me-text">If you can put your trust in me and consistently follow my instructions and
                        method I can guarantee that you will achieve your physical goals and become the best version of
                        yourself. </p>
                    <h4 class="p-title">The Choice Is Always Yours </h4>
                    <p class="about-me-text">Since there's no magic button we can push to reach our goals, we have to
                        decide
                        how bad we want our results. To achieve your goals, you have to be locked in and committed. I've
                        created plans based on my own personal training experiences and it's proven to give results. Are
                        you
                        willing to meet me halfway and become my next success story?</p>

